labels.privacy label detail:
The generative model is differentially private with a global privacy loss of (ε=10, δ=1e-5).

Each marginal distribution is first trained with simple DP histograms.
Then the global model is trained using DP-SGD.
The composition of all DP mechanisms is realized with a Renyi-DP accountant.

Because the generative model is DP, all rows of data generated share the same property (post processing).
